Features - Replace Text + Icons

Evaluate
Use the mobile app to rapidly evaluate athletes during training sessions and match sessions. Evaluate real-time and objectively during match sessions or using a simple grading scale.

Manage and Review
The simple dashboard allows you to track player development and understand the effectiveness of your curriculum. Compare player development across your team and/or organization.

Communicate
Easily share progress reports with players and parents. Players log in and view their individual profile to view evaluations and communicate with the coach. Parents now receive a friendly report card with objective feedback on their kids development.

Integrate
Save time by quickly importing player profiles from existing services like teamsnap or by using our simple data import features.
